sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Dashboard as ODH Dashboard<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Notebook as Jupyter Notebook<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Trainer as Kubeflow Trainer<br/>JobSet
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MR as Model Registry<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KServe as KServe Controller
    participant Predictor as Inference Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Gateway as Istio Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Client as External Client

    Note over User,Client: Workflow 1: Model Training to Deployment

    User->>Dashboard: Login (OAuth)
    Dashboard-->>User: Dashboard UI

    User->>Dashboard: Create Notebook Workbench
    Dashboard->>Notebook: Deploy StatefulSet
    Notebook-->>User: JupyterLab Interface

    User->>Notebook: Develop & Train Model
    Notebook->>MLflow: Log Experiment<br/>Bearer Token
    MLflow->>S3: Store Artifacts<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Notebook->>S3: Save Model<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Notebook->>MR: Register Model Metadata<br/>gRPC/9090
    MR-->>Notebook: Model ID

    User->>Dashboard: Create InferenceService
    Dashboard->>KServe: POST InferenceService CR<br/>K8s API
    KServe->>S3: Download Model<br/>TLS 1.2+
    KServe->>Predictor: Deploy Predictor Pod<br/>Knative
    KServe->>Gateway: Create VirtualService<br/>Istio

    Note over User,Client: Workflow 2: Distributed Training

    User->>Dashboard: Submit TrainJob
    Dashboard->>Trainer: Create TrainJob CR
    Trainer->>S3: Download Dataset<br/>HTTPS/443
    Trainer->>S3: Download Base Model<br/>HTTPS/443
    Trainer->>Trainer: Create JobSet<br/>Multi-node pods
    Note over Trainer: NCCL inter-pod<br/>communication
    Trainer->>MLflow: Log Metrics<br/>Bearer Token
    Trainer->>S3: Save Fine-tuned Model<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Trainer->>MR: Register Model<br/>gRPC/9090

    Note over User,Client: Workflow 3: Inference Request

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.3
    Gateway->>Predictor: Forward Request<br/>mTLS (optional)
    Predictor->>S3: Load Model (if needed)<br/>HTTPS/443
    Predictor-->>Gateway: Prediction Result<br/>JSON
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS Response<br/>TLS 1.3

    Note over User,Client: Workflow 4: Feature Store Integration

    User->>Notebook: Engineer Features
    Notebook->>Feast: Register FeatureView<br/>HTTP/6572
    Feast-->>Notebook: Confirmed

    User->>Trainer: Train with Features
    Trainer->>Feast: Fetch Historical Features<br/>HTTP/8815
    Feast-->>Trainer: Feature Data
    Trainer->>S3: Save Trained Model

    Client->>Gateway: Inference Request
    Gateway->>Predictor: Forward
    Predictor->>Feast: Get Online Features<br/>HTTP/6566
    Feast-->>Predictor: Real-time Features
    Predictor-->>Gateway: Prediction
    Gateway-->>Client: Response
